---
import { Image } from '@astrojs/image/components';
---
<section id="about" class="py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">About Digital Helper</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
      <div class="md:w-1/2 mb-8 md:mb-0">
        <Image
          src="/team-photo.jpg"
          alt="Digital Helper Team"
          width={600}
          height={400}
          format="webp"
          class="rounded-lg shadow-md"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          At Digital Helper, we're passionate about empowering businesses to thrive in the digital landscape. Our team of experts combines creativity with data-driven strategies to deliver exceptional results for our clients.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          With years of experience and a commitment to staying ahead of industry trends, we're your trusted partner in navigating the ever-evolving world of digital marketing.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>